title: prepaid card industry
extract: A prepaid cards processor is a company that processes transactions for prepaid payment cards. Prepaid card processors are responsible for processing transactions for prepaid credit or debit cards, gift cards, payroll cards, and other payment cards that are considered secured by the front-loading of money.Jun 23, 2018
